    <item>
      <title>News: Arturia Collection X</title>
      <link>https://jamesm.blog/music-production/news/arturia-v-collection-x/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 09:53:39 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://jamesm.blog/music-production/news/arturia-v-collection-x/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/&#34;&gt;[Arturia]&lt;/a&gt; have just released &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-instruments/v-collection/overview/&#34;&gt;V Collection X&lt;/a&gt; - A premium suite of software instruments for unparalleled sonic exploration; from evocative emulations and hybrid synth engines, to authentically modeled keyboards and beautifully captured acoustic sounds - enhanced for today’s production workflow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Immerse yourself in an unparalleled music-making experience with iconic sounds and essential tools to suit your style, performance needs and production workflow. 39 instruments, 3 exclusive expansion packs, thousands of world-class presets - 1 canvas for infinite sonic exploration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>News: Arturia FX Collection 4</title>
      <link>https://jamesm.blog/music-production/news/arturia-fx-collection-4/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Jun 2023 09:53:39 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://jamesm.blog/music-production/news/arturia-fx-collection-4/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/&#34;&gt;[Arturia]&lt;/a&gt; have just released &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-effects/fx-collection/overview/&#34;&gt;FX Collection 4&lt;/a&gt; which now includes &lt;strong&gt;30&lt;/strong&gt; effects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is currently an intro offer, you can get &lt;strong&gt;40% off&lt;/strong&gt; until 20th June 2023&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;List price: £429&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discounted price: &lt;strong&gt;£257&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; If you&amp;rsquo;re an owner of other Arturia products you will likely get an even bigger discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following effects have been added since collection 3;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-effects/rotary-cls-222/overview/&#34;&gt;Rotary CLS-222&lt;/a&gt; - reimagines the classic Dynacord® rotary speaker emulator as a creative plugin that goes from silky smooth stereo swirls to spinning synchronized patterns - enhancing your sound with extra width, momentum, and analog character in seconds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-effects/dist-coldfire/overview/&#34;&gt;Dist COLDFIRE&lt;/a&gt; - dual-engine distortion effect that goes from rich tube saturation to unrestrained sonic destruction in a few clicks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-effects/filter-ms-20/overview/&#34;&gt;Filter MS-20&lt;/a&gt; - stereo filter and distortion effect modeled on the infamously abrasive MS-20 synthesizer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-effects/rev-lx-24/overview/&#34;&gt;Rev LX-24&lt;/a&gt; - an enhanced virtual replica of a retro ambience box that defined reverb for a generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full details can be found &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.arturia.com/products/software-effects/fx-collection/overview/&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
